tiler (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Tiler
  * Complete X11 window tiling functionality
  * Support for horizontal, vertical, and grid tiling modes
  * Application-specific window filtering with -a/--for-app
  * Aspect ratio control with -r/--aspect-ratio
  * Configurable margins with -m/--margin
  * Robust X11 integration using python-xlib
  * Command-line interface with comprehensive help
  * Desktop integration with .desktop file and AppData

 -- Lenik <tiler@bodz.net>  Sat, 28 Dec 2025 23:30:00 +0800
